Maddalena Bellin, Chiara Alexandra Young

Info sketch TouchDesigner

General info
This sketch generates an audioreactive particle animation. The movement of the particles in the visuals is a reaction to different sound waves in the audio input. 
We were able to export frames and use them as an overlay throughout our design.

Credits
Bileam Tschepe, Audioreactive Particle Cloud
